    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         VS 2026 FLUENT DESIGN TOKENS
         Shell category: semantic Fluent tokens for controls, text, backgrounds.
         ShellInternal category: IDE chrome, title bar, status bar.
         VS 2022 ignores both categories gracefully (unknown GUIDs).
         VS 2026 reads these first, falls back to the categories above for
